OL,3,CHealthcare services in Wales remain
OL,4,Cunder 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FInspectors have warned that healthcare
OL,7,Fservice in Wales are facing "sustained
OL,8,Fpressure" with patients experiencing
OL,9,Fdelays.
OL,11,FAn annual report from the Healthcare
OL,12,FInspectorate Wales (HIW) detailed
OL,13,Fproblems with workforce shortages,
OL,14,Fovercrowding and long waiting times in
OL,15,Femergency departments.
