OL,3,CHealthcare services in Wales remain
OL,4,Cunder 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FInspectors said they received more
OL,7,Fthan 600 reports of concern this year,
OL,8,Fand engaged with more than 8,200
OL,9,Fpatients, staff, and carers to gain
OL,10,Finsights into their experiences with
OL,11,Fhealthcare services.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government said it welcomes
OL,14,Fthe report that shows "a service under
OL,15,Fpressure" and will consider the
OL,16,Ffindings.
