OL,3,CHealthcare services in Wales remain
OL,4,Cunder 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FDespite the pressures that the NHS and
OL,7,Fother healthcare services in Wales
OL,8,Fface, HIW has identified positive
OL,9,Finitiatives that are aimed at
OL,10,Fimproving urgent and out-of-hours care.
OL,12,FHIW listed new systems, including
OL,13,Falternative options for patients in
OL,14,Fneed of urgent care, that have been
OL,15,Fdeveloped to ease the strain on
OL,16,Femergency departments.
