OL,3,CHealthcare services in Wales remain
OL,4,Cunder 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FAlun Jones, Chief Executive of HIW,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our 2023-2024 annual report
OL,8,Fhighlights both the strengths and
OL,9,Fchallenges within the healthcare
OL,10,Fsystem in Wales.
OL,12,F"We have seen many positive
OL,13,Fdevelopments, particularly in areas
OL,14,Flike urgent care, but there are still
OL,15,Fsignificant pressures that need to be
OL,16,Faddressed, especially around capacity
OL,17,Fand patient flow.
