OL,3,CHealthcare services in Wales remain
OL,4,Cunder 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,F"Our role is to ensure that healthcare
OL,7,Fservices continue to deliver safe,
OL,8,Feffective care, and we remain
OL,9,Fcommitted to driving improvements
OL,10,Fwhere they are most needed.
OL,12,F"I want to thank all the healthcare
OL,13,Fstaff, patients, and organisations who
OL,14,Fhave contributed to our work
OL,15,Fthroughout the year. Their insights
OL,16,Fare invaluable in helping us improve
OL,17,Fhealthcare in Wales."
