OL,3,CHealthcare services in Wales remain
OL,4,Cunder 'sustained pressure'
OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We welcome this report from
OL,8,FHealthcare Inspectorate Wales, and we
OL,9,Fwill consider the findings in due
OL,10,Fcourse.
OL,12,F"The report clearly shows a service
OL,13,Funder pressure, and we recognise
OL,14,Ffurther work is needed to improve
OL,15,Faccess to and people's experience of
OL,16,FNHS services. We continue to work
OL,17,Fclosely with health boards and NHS
OL,18,Ftrusts to improve services."
